snippet.textDisplay:
I have some suggestions.

First, I would like if they made a co-op mode (2 characters for any player and 1 character for the other player // Or one character for each player). It could be online or against CPU (inside some a new mode).

Second, I think it should be possible to choose all the characters at once in the tournament mode. It is very boring have to back to the character screen between each fight.

Third, they should introduce a new mode, in which each player could choose 10 characters at once. The fight would be 3 x 3 yet, but if one character is down, the respective next would take her place immediately, until the end. It would be awesome.
